headline.print_headline: QPR Edge Wigan in Extra Time to Reach Playoff Final
headline.main: QPR Edge Wigan in Extra Time to Reach Playoff Final

lead_paragraph: Charlie Austin scored twice including the extra-time winner to drag Queens Park Rangers into the English Championship (second tier) playoff final after a 2-1 comeback victory against Wigan Athletic on Monday.
